*lxpanel-0.8.1 (17 May 2015)

  17 May 2015; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> +lxpanel-0.8.1.ebuild:
  Version bump thanks to jospezial. Bug #524654

  03 Mar 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> lxpanel-0.7.0-r1.ebuild:
  add arm64 support, tested on A53 board

  08 Jan 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> lxpanel-0.7.0-r1.ebuild:
  Require USE=gtk on libfm, https://bugs.funtoo.org/browse/FL-1932.

*lxpanel-0.7.0-r1 (10 Sep 2014)

  10 Sep 2014; Pavel Kazakov <nullishzero@gentoo.org>
  +files/lxpanel-0.7.0-right-click-fix.patch, +lxpanel-0.7.0-r1.ebuild:
  Patch for fixing left-click issue, thanks to Jonathan Thibault for bug report
  (Bug #522404). Also looks as if >=x11-libs/libfm-1.2.0 is a hard dependency
  now.

*lxpanel-0.7.0 (06 Sep 2014)

  06 Sep 2014; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> +lxpanel-0.7.0.ebuild:
  Version bump. Bug #518134. x11-libs/libwnck does not seem to be optional
  anymore

